They are embedded in electromechanical devices, sensors.
You need to decode the way you want to fold into a series of angles -- minus 120 degrees, minus 120 degrees, 0 degrees, 0 degrees, 120 degrees, minus 120 degrees -- things like that; a series of angles, or turns, that can be passed through with wires.
